00:42:02.230 --> 00:42:03.760
Hindi ba dapat malalim ang sasabihin mo?

00:42:03.760 --> 00:42:05.360
Sa Gorky's
"The Song of the Stormy Petrel,"

00:42:05.360 --> 00:42:06.960
may linya na napupunta...

00:42:10.030 --> 00:42:10.840
sabi nito,

00:42:12.230 --> 00:42:14.550
kapag ang mga tao ay nahaharap sa kahirapan sa buhay,

00:42:15.110 --> 00:42:17.030
dapat silang maging tulad ng bagyong petrel,

00:42:17.030 --> 00:42:18.430
lumilipad patungo sa bagyo,

00:42:18.540 --> 00:42:20.070
at lumulutang na may nakabukang mga pakpak.

00:42:20.070 --> 00:42:20.800
yun lang!

00:42:21.310 --> 00:42:22.690
Sa amin, dalawang mabagyong petrel!

00:42:22.690 --> 00:42:24.620
Salimbay na may nakabukang mga pakpak.

00:42:32.570 --> 00:42:33.300
Masarap.

00:42:38.360 --> 00:42:39.360
Propesor Xiang.

00:42:39.860 --> 00:42:41.590
I must say, medyo matapang ka.

00:42:43.360 --> 00:42:44.400
Ang ganitong uri ng kalan

00:42:44.610 --> 00:42:45.870
madaling masunog.

00:42:46.090 --> 00:42:47.560
Ang silid na ito ay maaaring magliyab,

00:42:47.560 --> 00:42:49.280
at maaari mong sunugin
ang buong gusali.

00:42:49.280 --> 00:42:50.480
Medyo extreme yun.

00:42:50.960 --> 00:42:51.960
Paano ito extreme?

00:42:53.100 --> 00:42:54.430
Sa aming paaralan noon,

00:42:55.480 --> 00:42:56.690
dahil sa ganitong uri ng kalan,

00:42:56.690 --> 00:42:57.640
dalawang tao ang namatay.

00:42:59.190 --> 00:43:01.360
At kumakain din sila ng noodles.

00:43:02.840 --> 00:43:04.280
Instant noodles din.

00:43:05.220 --> 00:43:05.900
Isang lalaki

00:43:06.190 --> 00:43:06.920
at isang babae.

00:43:07.920 --> 00:43:09.360
Pati yung lalaki

00:43:09.360 --> 00:43:11.090
nakaupo sa kama ng ganito.

00:43:11.360 --> 00:43:13.480
At ang babae ay may buhok
na kapareho ng haba ko...

00:43:13.480 --> 00:43:14.080
ayos lang.

00:43:14.100 --> 00:43:14.970
Tumigil ka sa pagsasalita. Mangyaring huminto.

00:43:14.970 --> 00:43:16.300
Tanggalin ko sa pagkakasaksak ito ngayon.

